%% Helix OTA — Device update sequence (canonical)
%% Source of truth: 00-master/2026-06-07-helix-ota-design.md §5 (MVP happy path)
%% Consistent with: 1.0.0-mvp/api/endpoints.md §12.1 (204/200 branch), §12.2 (telemetry),
%%                   1.0.0-mvp/security/signing_verification.md §6 (device re-verify before apply)
%% poll -> update -> apply -> reboot -> verify -> telemetry, with the 204/200 update-check branch.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant AG as OTA agent (ota-android-agent)
    participant API as Control plane (Gin /api/v1)
    participant OBJ as Storage (MinIO/S3)
    participant UE as update_engine + boot_control
    participant TEL as Telemetry ingest

    Note over AG,API: Poll cadence 15 min + jitter (configurable, D7)
    AG->>API: GET /api/v1/client/update [device bearer, current_version]

    alt 204 No Content (already on target version)
        API-->>AG: 204 No Content (no body)
        Note over AG: Idle until next poll
    else 200 OK (update assigned)
        API-->>AG: 200 OK UpdateAvailable {url, offset, size, sha256, signature, payload_properties}
        AG->>TEL: POST /client/telemetry event=download_started
        AG->>OBJ: Range GET artifact (Content-Encoding: identity, ZIP_STORED, byte-identical)
        OBJ-->>AG: 206 Partial Content (payload bytes)
        AG->>TEL: POST /client/telemetry event=download_complete

        Note over AG: GATE 2 — device re-verify before apply
        AG->>AG: recompute SHA-256 (+SHA-512) and verify detached signature by key_id

        alt verification fails (hash/signature)
            AG->>TEL: POST /client/telemetry event=failure (HASH_MISMATCH / SIGNATURE_INVALID)
            Note over AG: Abort before apply — no slot touched
        else verified local artifact
            AG->>UE: applyPayload(file://verified, offset, size, payload_properties)
            AG->>TEL: POST /client/telemetry event=installing
            Note over UE: GATE 3 — FILE_HASH / METADATA_HASH + payload signature
            UE-->>AG: applied to inactive slot
            AG->>TEL: POST /client/telemetry event=installed
            AG->>UE: mark inactive slot active + reboot
            Note over UE: Reboot into new slot

            alt boot success (update_verifier confirms)
                Note over UE: GATE 4 — AVB / dm-verity verified boot OK
                AG->>TEL: POST /client/telemetry event=verifying
                AG->>TEL: POST /client/telemetry event=success
            else boot failure
                Note over UE: Automatic A/B rollback to last-good slot (native, no Helix metadata)
                AG->>TEL: POST /client/telemetry event=rollback
                AG->>TEL: POST /client/telemetry event=failure
            end
        end
    end
    TEL-->>AG: 202 Accepted (async ingest)
